				\begin{document}$$v_\pi \left( s \right) = {\Bbb E}_\pi \left[ {\mathop {{{\mathrm{lim}}}}\limits_{T \to \infty } \frac{{\mathop {\sum}\nolimits_{t = 0}^T {\gamma ^tr_t} }}{{\mathop {\sum}\nolimits_{t = 0}^T {\gamma ^t} }}\left| {S_0 = s} \right.} \right].$$\end{document}vπs=EπlimT→∞∑t=0Tγtrt∑t=0TγtS0=s.

